    {
      "chinese": "因為布農族的家人人數都很多，所以布農族人蓋的家屋都很長。用石板蓋屋頂和用石頭堆圍牆。在屋頂做一個天窗，讓家裡能夠曬到陽光。",
      "ab": "Maupa i katpipia dau itu Bunun tu tastulumaq bunun, paaqpun, madadauqpus isia Bunun tu sinkalumaq. Makusia bistav masu’ia tavi siin maku’uni batu malqutun sinbalung. Matas’i haan tavi ki tungkul, namaqtu sanvali’un a lumaq kumbu.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2020/12/21/38b8e8fe30cd2f6f7e79f6be6905fabb.wav",
